  ;;   primitive #1 graph carries source TypeHandles through into LowExpr
  ;;   records (LMakeList/LMakeTuple/LMakeRecord/LMakeVariant/LIf/LBlock/
  ;;   LMatch/LFieldLoad/LUnaryOp/LMakeClosure):
