  ;;           [lo_else]. Per wheel src/lower.nx:369-372 canonical.
  ;;           lexpr.wat:455-467 LIf field 2/3 are List per src/lower.nx:121
  ;;           LIf(Int, LowExpr, List, List) — current parser_compound.wat:
